VLGal/Directory $Revision: 0.01 $
===============================

SHORT DESCRIPTION

The modules in VLGal form an API to generate a simple HTML
orianted gallery of photos.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Error

